extends layout/layout
block content
  section.hero(aria-label='Image of a person sitting on the floor with their back on a couch while using a laptop to study. Photo by Thought Catalog on Unsplash')
    .hero__container.container.h-100.position-relative
      .hero__content.position-absolute
        h1.hero__title Quick, Easy, Study in a Flash!
        p.hero__copy Studying made easy with FlashCard. Create your own flashcards and study them online. 
        a.btn.btn--primary.btn--large(href='/register') Sign up
  section.section.section-feature.pt-5.pb-4
    .container.d-md-flex
      .section__header.w-md-50  
        img(
          class='img',
          alt='Image of a person studying using a laptop. Photo by Kojo Kwarteng on Unsplash',
          src='static/img/kojo-kwarteng-KUzlAah2dog-unsplash.jpg'
        )
      .section__content.w-md-50.p-3
        .container
          .section__content-header
            h2.section__content-title.my-3 Studying Made Easy
          .section__content-body.pb-4 
            p.section__content-copy.m-0
              | Flashcard allows you to create your own flashcards to study from. 
              | Sign-up is free and is easy to get started.    
  section.section.section-feature.section-feature--alt.pt-4.pb-3
    .container.d-md-flex.flex-md-row-reverse
      .section__header.w-md-50
        img(
          class='img',
          atl='Image of a person studying using a laptop. Photo by Anete Lūsiņa on Unsplash',
          src='static/img/anete-lusina--4Wi_ii6StY-unsplash.jpg'
        )
      .section__content.w-md-50.p-3
        .container
          .section__content-header
            h2.section__content-title.my-3 Save Time
          .section__content-body.pb-4
            p.section__content-copy.m-0
              | Spend more time studing and lease time writing out your notes.
              | 